{"tid":1134704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公園內用丫义射白鴿 男子涉殘酷對待動物被捕","createTime":"2019-05-02T00:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T01:07:23.000Z","uid":3090,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8525132c0a01ae2e36ec47d00d60cf25c8e68e81","tid":1134704,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFQqLV4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFQqLV4.png&h=14a8399f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南昌公園下午發生一宗懷疑殘酷對待動物案件。姜偉康攝<br />\n<br />\n下午5時許，有途人發現一名男子在深水埗南昌公園用丫义射草叢內的白鴿，警方接報到場調查，以涉嫌殘酷對待動物拘捕一名36歲姓溫男子，案件由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"3a06e48b2f986954fd4a0901a526aaae5975746b","tid":1134704,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:20:46.000Z","msg":"可唔可以拉埋哩件<br />\n<br />\nUST 內地女生虐打同住人嘅貓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1132346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1132346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af63c42595b5f9220a6d444cf21850befef28e4a","tid":1134704,"uid":57844,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:21:12.000Z","msg":"on9 政府，想食乳鴿都唔比"},{"pid":"0d987f60489d313d1ca5a0e776494d4844a1cddf","tid":1134704,"uid":168366,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af63c42595b5f9220a6d444cf21850befef28e4a","tid":1134704,"uid":57844,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:21:12.000Z","msg":"on9 政府，想食乳鴿都唔比"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:29:59.000Z","msg":"好好笑?"},{"pid":"befdc9b058cec475ee39eb2ec6be593027b1ed2f","tid":1134704,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:32:16.000Z","msg":"支那人通常都一定冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad13c0592495980594e705c12773ee8ea6fc1b2","tid":1134704,"uid":226587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:32:41.000Z","msg":"漁農署射野豬又得？"},{"pid":"03246e7453c36a68e1b608b6712d9a8f39ba75